name: Conference BridgeTelephone Number
title: CB TEL NO
definition: Identifies the Conference Bridge Telephone number to be used at the time of implementation or cut over.
usageNotes: Prohibited when the first position of the REQTYP   field is “A” “R” or “W” otherwise optional.
fieldNotes: The time allocated for the implementation/cut over   activity will be specified in the Frame Due Time   (FDT) field on the ASR.
